===Noun===
{{en-noun}}

# Putting text into the Latin (Roman) [[alphabet]], by means such as [[transliteration]] and [[transcription]].

====Usage notes====
* ''Latin [[transliteration]]'' refers to the romanization of text in an [[alphabetic]] script, but not for the romanization of text in a [[logographic]] script, especially as for many Asian languages.

